Schemes:
   A(a,b)
   R(a,b)
   S(A,B,C)

Facts:
   R('1','2').
   A('1','1').
   A('1','2').
   A('2','3').
   A('3','4').
   A('4','5').
S('4','4','1').
S('4','3','1').

Rules: 
   R(X,X):-A(X,'1').
   R(X,X):-A(X,'2').
   S(X,Y,Z):-S(X,Y,Z).
   A(X,Y):-A(X,X).
	
Queries:
   R(x,y)?
R(x,y)?
R(x,y)?
R(x,y)?
S(X,X,'1')?